420
00:24:35,780 --> 00:24:37,210
I'm fine.

421
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:38,830
Why do you ask?

422
00:24:40,700 --> 00:24:41,830
That photo.

423
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:44,950
Why are you thinking about Guo Yan?

424
00:24:48,020 --> 00:24:49,190
I told you

425
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:50,910
