to be controlled by my family.

495
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,390
That's all.

496
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:16,860
I'll help you.

497
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:26,630
Just passing is enough.

498
00:30:26,630 --> 00:30:27,500
Suit yourself.

499
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:34,260
